text: Refined Brownstone Living in the Heart of Southlake Town Square Discover elevated urban living in this stunning Southlake Town Square brownstonea thoughtfully designed residence blending upscale elegance, smart architecture, and unbeatable walkability in one of DFWs most coveted communities. Just steps from world-class shopping, dining, and entertainment, this luxurious retreat offers the perfect balance of vibrancy and privacy behind its stately faade. An open-concept floor plan sets the stage for effortless living and entertaining, with rich hardwood floors, and abundant natural light throughout. The designer kitchen impresses with custom cabinetry, premium appliances, while the living and dining areas open seamlessly to a resort-style courtyard featuring a pristine plunge pool, fire bowls, your own private oasis. The entire second floor is dedicated to a luxurious primary suite, complete with a spa-inspired bath, oversized bedroom, and a custom 23 x 10 boutique-style closet. The third-floor media room offers flexible space for entertainment or relaxation along with open flex space and two bedrooms Above the detached garage is a fully private guest suite with its own entrance and en-suite bathideal for extended stays, an office, or studio. Every detail in this home exudes quality, from designer-selected finishes to smart home features and custom touches throughout. Located within the award-winning Carroll ISD and walkable to everything Southlake Town Square has to offer, this exceptional brownstone delivers the ultimate in low-maintenance, high-style living.

text: Lonesome Dove Estates is a very popular neighborhood in an unbeatable location away from high traffic areas, yet close to everything Southlake has to offer. At 1203 Powder River youll find a ONE STORY with an upstairs Bonus Room, 4 Bedrooms, three Full Baths, a Formal Living and Formal Dining all featuring new flooring which even includes all new baseboards. The Bonus Room could be a third living, game room, or theater room, located above the 3 car garage which provides privacy and sound reduction. The updates are endless...In addition to new paint throughout, including the garage, other updates include a remodeled Kitchen with Counter Height Breakfast Bar, Level 3 Granite, Stainless Appliances and newly finished Cabinetry with soft close doors - The Family Room includes an ultra-modern fireplace with ample area for your BIG flat screen TV. ALL BATHS have been TOTALLY remodeled --we're talking floors, fixtures, Quartz Counter tops, glass showers and more...All bedrooms are large and have walk-in closets. The Primary Closet has been remodeled creating lots of usable space. From the Kitchen, breakfast and living room area, theres a view of the spacious backyard featuring a pool area with lots of decking for entertainment and a covered patio for cooling off after a day of fun in the sun or for watching the sunrise to start your day. Located on the north side within 5 minutes of Grapevine Lake and Southlake Town Square, youll appreciate the easy access to major highways, Historic Downtown Grapevine, DFW Airport and beyond while missing the high volume traffic areas to get there. Of course, included in the package is the Southlake Carroll ISD featuring the CARROLL DRAGONS!!!. There isn't enough space here to list everything special about 1203 Powder River, so you'll just need to come see for yourself.

text: Theres a quiet rhythm to life on Helmsley Place. From the moment you walk through the door, theres a sense of welcome. The entry opens into sunlit spaces that stretch out with ease, grounded by warm hardwood floors and a floor plan designed for real life. text: Timeless French inspired architecture meets contemporary luxury at 225 Murano. Gracefully situated in the prestigious Carillon Parc community, 225 Murano is a striking 4, 816 square foot custom home that redefines elevated living. Designed and built by award winning builder Atwood Custom Homes, This 5 bedroom, 5.5 bathroom residence offers a perfect balance of bold design, comfortable function and ultimate luxury living. Step inside to sophisticated interiors that unfold across an open concept floor plan featuring a kitchen including professional-grade appliances, an island that opens to the dining area and sweeps you into the living space to cozy up to the fireplace on those chilly evenings. A prep kitchen for all your entertaining needs. Primary suite along with the guest quarters located on the first level for ease and accessibility. Look no further for the inviting flex room as you enter the home for any family meeting spaces you might be wanting to gather in every weekend. Designer lighting and floor-to-ceiling windows that flood the home with natural light. On the second level you will find 3 additional bedrooms, all thoughtfully positioned to offer privacy, with ensuite baths and generous closets, a laundry room upstairs for the ultimate convenience and a loft for guests to settle in for the night watching a favorite show or reading a book before bed. Located in one of Southlake's most anticipated lifestyle communities, 225 Murano places you in the heart of Southlake's finest dining, boutique shopping, green spaces and community amenities-all designed to bring elegance and convenience to everyday life. Request your personal consultation with the builder to discover how 225 Murano can be yours.

Welcome to 1520 Moss Lane, a stunning custom estate in the gated community of Moss Farms in Southlake. Set on over an acre in Carroll ISD, this 5, 746 sq ft home offers timeless design, luxury finishes, and thoughtful functionality throughout. The home features four spacious ensuite bedrooms with walk-in closets, four full baths, and two powder baths. The primary suite is a serene retreat with a private sitting area, spa-inspired bath with dual vanities, dual water closets, walk-in shower with body sprays, and a custom closet with direct access to the laundry room. Elegant limestone tile flooring runs through the main living areas. The family room boasts real cypress wood ceilings and a full masonry fireplace with a marble mantle. The chefs kitchen is equipped with two oversized islands, quartzite countertops, commercial-grade appliances, real cypress wood beams, and two pantries. A formal dining room with butlers pantry and a bright breakfast room complete the space. A dedicated office, additional workspace in the laundry room, and a game and theater room with full bar offer ideal spaces for work and play. Smart home features, electric shades, built-in speakers, and designer lighting enhance everyday living. Enjoy year-round outdoor entertaining with a covered patio, fireplace, electric screens, built-in grill, and a pizza oven. The oversized jacuzzi and tranquil water feature complete the backyard oasis. Adjacent to a heavily wooded greenbelt, the property offers privacy and natural beauty. Additional highlights include a four-car garage, full-house generator, and a fully encapsulated ~1, 750 sq ft walk-up attic ready to be finished. This home is a rare opportunity to own a true luxury estate in one of Southlakes most sought-after communities.

text: Discover the perfect blend of sophisticated living and urban convenience with this exquisite brownstone located in the highly sought-after Southlake Town Square. Offering a rare opportunity to enjoy walkability to the area's most celebrated restaurants, boutique shops, movie theaters, and scenic parks, this property is ideal for those who value both luxury and lifestyle. From the moment you arrive, youll appreciate the timeless architecture and thoughtfully curated design elements that define this beautiful home. Inside, an elevator conveniently services all floors, providing ease of access while adding a layer of comfort and prestige to everyday living. Spacious, light-filled living areas feature high-end finishes, quality craftsmanship, and a layout perfectly suited for both relaxed living and elegant entertaining. Step outside into the beautifully designed private courtyard a true sanctuary. Meticulously landscaped and finished with premium materials, this inviting outdoor space is perfect for morning coffee, al fresco dining, or gathering with friends under the stars. The courtyard seamlessly connects the main residence to the detached garage, where you'll find a charming guest quarters above ideal for visiting family, a dedicated work-from-home space, or an au pair suite, offering privacy and flexibility. The primary suite serves as a luxurious retreat, complete with spa-inspired amenities and generous closet space. Additional bedrooms are equally well-appointed, providing comfort for family and guests alike. Situated just minutes from major highways and offering quick, easy access to DFW International Airport, this location is a commuters dream, whether for business or leisure. Yet, with everything you could need right outside your door, you may find little reason to leave.

text: Set on a private, north-facing lot in one of Southlakes most desirable pockets, 309 Woodsong Way offers a rare combination: a single-story custom home with architectural character, uncompromising quality, and a layout designed for modern living, all within walking distance to Southlake Town Square and zoned to coveted Carroll ISD. text: Discover elegance and authenticity in this stunning custom home nestled in a distinguished Southlake community, perfect for both raising a family and entertaining. This home showcases European flair and robust construction, ensuring a blend of grandeur and security without the hassle of a Homeowners Association. Covering an impressive 6, 062 sq ft, this home features five bedrooms and five bathrooms. The master suite and guest bedroom are conveniently located on the first floor, while three more bedrooms await upstairs, providing ample space for your family. Each room is equipped with built in storage and accented with vintage Ralph Lauren wallpaper, custom crown molding, and trophy shelving ideal for celebratory displays. The chefs gourmet kitchen is a culinary dream, featuring top of the line Thermador appliances, two dishwashers, a commercial disposal, and a versatile range with both gas burners and griddle alongside four ovens. An oversized island and a sizable pantry complement the space beautifully, ensuring you have everything you need to host and entertain. The formal living room, office, and study area offer scenic views of the propertys lush landscape and luxury diving pool. Outdoor living is equally grand, with a pristine Pavestone entry, handmade gas lamps, and nearly half an acre to design your perfect outdoor haven or cabana. The homes prime location offers easy access to exceptional local schooling, with Old Union Elementary, Eubanks Intermediate School, and Dawson Middle School within walking distance. Enjoy a splendid array of nearby amenities, including generous parks and playgrounds, prestigious shopping at Southlake Town Square, and effortless commuting options to major destinations. Grant yourself the lifestyle you deserve in this serene and opulent Southlake home, where comfort meets quintessential luxury. Whether you're hosting lavish parties or enjoying quiet evenings by the pool, this home invites you to live remarkably.
